  <brief_title>Effect of Meal Texture on Glucose-metabolism and Gut Hormone Response After Bariatric Surgery</brief_title>
  <acronym>Obesity</acronym>
  <official_title>Does Meal Texture Have Different Impact on Glucose Metabolism and Intestinal Hormone Response After Gastric Bypass and Sleeve Gastrectomy Operated Patients?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
